-Gkaljaow.description: Michael Scarn is one of Michael Scott's most common improv characters and the main hero of his movie, Threat Level Midnight.
-Gkaljaow.title: Agent Michael Scarn

-Gaoaowihw.description: Prison Mike is Michael's prison character when he finds out that Martin is a convict. In his Prison Mike persona, Michael paints an awful, and somewhat fanciful, picture of prison life.
-Gaoaowihw.title: Prison Mike

-GpaisgeoJ.description: Date Mike is a rowdy and wild persona that Michael Scott adopts when he goes on a date. However, Michael is unaware that the Date Mike persona is unappealing.
-GpaisgeoJ.title: Date Mike
